cellmate.extractor
Class SingleMultiValueCellExtractor

Object
  SingleMultiValueCellExtractor
All Implemented Interfaces:
CellExtractor
@Beta
public class SingleMultiValueCellExtractor
extends Object
implements CellExtractor

Basic extractor implementation that offers cell filter capability by provided Predicate rules.
. This class contains methods that look through a cell group and return one or more cell(s) that match a given label. Specifically, there are methods that expect to find a single cell matching the label before returning the value. This implementation works across any cell class type annotated with Cell, but most of the methods additionally require additioanlly annoting your cell class with Label and Value. CellReflector
